strategy: There's no easier lane for Yone. Just don't fight her level 1 with Lethal Tempo because she is a lot stronger with it. You can perma all-in her whenever you want until level 6. She can't walk up to the wave early or she will get chunked. At level 6, it becomes a bit more difficult because of her range, but just get Q3s and all-in her with your E. If she ults, just E back and wait for your E to come up again and just all-in her again.
